== 6. Re1?! ==
An irregular sideline. White might be imagining '''6...Nf6?!''' 7. Nxe5{{chess/not|+}}. Instead, Black's best move is '''6...Nc5''', and White can't preserve the bishop pair. 

This leads to 7. Bxc6 dxc6 8. d4 Ne6 9. Nxe5 Be7 10. Be3 0-0 11. c4 and either 11...Bf6 or 11...Bd6, with an equal position.

